OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother mostly cloudy day over
OL,6,FShetland which may see a little patchy
OL,7,Frain at times. Generally brighter and
OL,8,Fwarmer conditions over Orkney before
OL,9,Fpatchy rain arrives towards the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,13,Fwith some patchy mainly light rain,
OL,14,Fand increasingly misty especially over
OL,15,FShetland. Winds mostly light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,18,Frain, some of this could turn heavier
OL,19,Flater but Shetland will turn dry in
OL,20,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
