OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FIt
OL,6,Fwill be a dry few days with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine, particularly for Shetland
OL,8,Fwith Orkney cloudier on Saturday.
OL,9,FWinds will be light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
